{"tid":693344,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"網上瘋傳天文台內部消息明日8號　天文台：惡作劇或變狼來了","createTime":"2018-06-07T11:37:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T12:03:05.000Z","uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"83854c69343a9e5c3679042999dc055624013db0","tid":693344,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:37:06.000Z","msg":"天文台內部消息明日8號？天文台今日(7日)中午12時40分改發3號強風信號，並已表明今日改發更高強風信號的機會較低。不過多個社交網站及網上討論區流傳「即將掛三號，明日八號」及「天文台內部天氣消息：聽日八號」等訊息，有市民當笑話轉發。天文台回覆TOPick查詢澄清，明日天氣情況仍是未知數，希望市民不要轉發錯誤信息，即使是惡作劇，也可能會造成「狠來了」效應。<br />\n<br />\n網上今早(7日)開始流傳，「天文台內部天氣消息：聽日八號」；亦有流傳是：「堅料！天文台朋友消息：星期五一定八號；星期日一定十號！」<br />\n<br />\n有人驟眼看以為又是打風謠言，但不少網民都知留言是惡作劇，純粹因為明天是8號，周日是10號，有網民批評這種笑話並不好笑："},{"pid":"8ce6d61d3132670e1dcf1c127c75eadee4149ddc","tid":693344,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"講到惡作劇 亂話機會不大點夠天文台玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd5fb99b5758e9ae69ddd5023e9cb26393b02197","tid":693344,"uid":14029,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"8ce6d61d3132670e1dcf1c127c75eadee4149ddc","tid":693344,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:37:58.000Z","msg":"講到惡作劇 亂話機會不大點夠天文台玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:42:36.000Z","msg":"系<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f61a12da0d574fd30687cf8368d4941abb15d6e","tid":693344,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"駛吾刀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"341ec0ea5988612fe1b0087dac30c55647d24803","tid":693344,"uid":4006,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"re